  "excerpt": "Nationwide spending on nonresidential construction decreased by 0.5% for March following weeks of uncertainty in the face of new trade tariffs, the latest analysis of U.S. Census Bureau data from the Associated Builders and Contractors has shown. On a seasonally adjusted annualized...",
